"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/54BOXpX2ieTXMDzHymdDMnUIzYG.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":6.042},{"width":1530,"height":861,"file_path":"/mOeBBD49M72vCEXzgA1dS2MwGno.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":5.25},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/bZlismAr366jWFiZNKzY3x3AN5X.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":4.722},{"width":3040,"height":1710,"file_path":"/vTxxMQk6ZOUSvcjBYIPjXRpInul.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":4},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/gFVLyx2EX9jrnV2RY8rF9Y3W9aH.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/igxgTccNiUGmIBVO9kjivuVPp52.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/1Z0nATltcUBA3Hvr4kWwptZJrPa.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/zBMyZzJtv3fwbztii7zFKgQVTaU.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/laWV5ohHOxYnCkvrJcZf6IDOIDO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/AdK8KnNsYTMlQYdCEV5lzGt3zE9.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3040,"height":1710,"file_path":"/s34HktbKlBBn1Q84G7bhpg3DkrB.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/gbOJy0sxjD99TODdXQ9b35tw45r.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/d6129HZoLlZC3pndxrkEKaKiqLW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/gtHUAhRKXhCBo35fN6yA9kSMfg8.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":1.75},{"width":1500,"height":844,"file_path":"/8lTtbtyDsBdvUtS95XlaJ97m8RQ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.5}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T06:01:37.947+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"You there?","homepage":"https://www.fivenightsatfreddys.movie","overview":"One year since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, the stories about what transpired there have been twisted into a campy local legend, inspiring the town's first ever Fazfest. With the truth kept from her, Abby sneaks out to reconnect with Freddy, Bonnie, Chica, and Foxy, setting into motion a terrifying series of events that will reveal dark secrets about the real origin of Freddy's, and unleash a decades-hidden horror."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"¿Estás ahí?","homepage":"","overview":"Un año después de los sucesos de Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, y con la llegada de un nuevo Faszfest al pueblo. Abby se escapa para reencontrarse con Freddy, Bonnie, Chica y Foxy con oscuros secretos revelándose."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Năm Đêm Kinh Hoàng 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"Bạn ở đó chứ?","homepage":"https://www.fivenightsatfreddys.movie","overview":"Một năm sau cơn ác mộng siêu nhiên tại tiệm Pizza Freddy Fazbear, những câu chuyện xoay quanh sự kiện ấy đã bị bóp méo thành một huyền thoại kỳ quặc tại địa phương, truyền cảm hứng cho lễ hội Fazfest đầu tiên của thị trấn. Không hề biết sự thật bị che giấu, Abby lén trốn ra ngoài để gặp lại Freddy, Bonnie, Chica và Foxy — khởi đầu cho chuỗi sự kiện kinh hoàng, hé lộ bí mật đen tối về nguồn gốc thật sự của Freddy’s, và đánh thức một nỗi kinh hoàng bị chôn vùi suốt hàng thập kỷ."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"ხუთი ღამე ფრედისთან 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ერთი წელი გავიდა ფრედის ფაზბერ პიცაში შემაძრწუნებელი სუპერნატურალური კოშმრის შემდეგ, იქ მომხდარი მოვლენების შესახებ ისტორიები კემპური ადგილობრივი ლეგენდის სახეს იძენენ, რაც ქალაქის პირველი ფაზფესტის ორგანიზებას უწყობს ხელს. იმის შესახებ, რაც მოხდა, ჭეშმარიტება მასგან დამალულია, აბი მალულად მიდის ფრედის, ბონი, ჩიკას და ფოქსის მოსანახულებლად, რამაც საშინელი მოვლენების სერია დაიწყო, რომელიც გამოავლენს ფრედის სინამდვილე წარმოშობის ბნელ საიდუმლოებებს და გააღვიძებს მათთვის საუკუნეების განმავლობაში დამალულ საშიშ კოშმარს."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"프레디의 피자가게 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"다시 밤이 되었습니다, 이제 밖으로 나가주세요","homepage":"","overview":"소문과 괴담에 휘말려 폐업한 ‘프레디의 피자가게’ 본점이 수십년 만에 다시 열리고, 그곳에 오랫동안 잠들어 있던 신형 프레디와 친구들이 눈을 뜨게 된다. 안면 인식 시스템을 가진 한층 더 기괴하고 오싹해진 신형 애니메트로닉스들은 이제 피자가게 밖으로 나와 세상을 공포에 몰아넣기 시작하는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"Qualquer um pode sobreviver cinco noites. Desta vez, não haverá segundas chances.","homepage":"https://www.universalpics.com.br/micro/five-nights-2","overview":"Um ano após o pesadelo sobrenatural na Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, as histórias sobre o que aconteceu ali foram distorcidas, transformando-se em uma lenda local exagerada, inspirando o primeiro Fazfest da cidade. Sem saber a verdade sobre o ocorrido, Abby sai escondida para se reconectar com Freddy, Bonnie, Chica e Foxy, dando início a uma aterrorizante série de eventos que revelarão segredos sombrios sobre a verdadeira origem da Freddy's e libertarão um horror há muito esquecido, escondido por décadas."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"ファイブ・ナイツ・アット・フレディーズ２","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un año después de la pesadilla sobrenatural en Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, las historias sobre lo ocurrido allí se han convertido en una leyenda local extravagante, inspirando el primer Fazfest del pueblo. Con la verdad oculta, Abby se escapa para reencontrarse con Freddy, Bonnie, Chica y Foxy, desencadenando una serie de eventos aterradores que revelarán oscuros secretos sobre el verdadero origen de Freddy's y desatarán un horror oculto durante décadas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Freddy'nin Pizza Dükkanında Beş Gece 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Freddy Fazbear's Pizza'daki korkunç olayın üzerinden bir yıl geçti. Şimdi bu hikayeler efsaneleşti ve ilk Fazfest düzenlendi. Abby, gerçeği öğrenmeden Freddy ve arkadaşlarıyla bağlantı kurmak için kaçıyor. Bu durum karanlık sırları açığa çıkaracak korkunç olayları başlatıyor."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ravi de vous revoir ! Prêts pour le grand spectacle ?","homepage":"https://www.universalpictures.fr/micro/five-nights-2","overview":"Un an s’est écoulé depuis le cauchemar surnaturel survenu chez Freddy Fazbear's Pizza. Un effroyable nouveau chapitre d'horreur s'ouvre lorsqu’Abby, la sœur de Mike, ancien agent de sécurité, s'échappe à la recherche de ses amis animatroniques : Freddy, Bonnie, Chica et Foxy. Alors que de terrifiants événements se déclenchent, de sombres secrets sur les véritables origines de Freddy sont révélés, libérant une horreur oubliée depuis des décennies."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"玩具熊的五夜惊魂2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"2023年《佛萊迪餐館之五夜驚魂》續集，伊莉莎白萊爾、喬許哈契遜、馬修利拉德主演。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Pet noći kod Fredija 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"Svatko može preživjeti pet noći. Ovaj put neće biti druge šanse.","homepage":"","overview":"Godinu dana nakon nadnaravne noćne more u pizzeriji Freddyja Fazbeara, priče o onome što se tamo dogodilo isprepletene su u lokalnu legendu koja je nadahnula prvi gradski Fazfest. S istinom o onome što se dogodilo skrivenom od nje, Abby se iskrada kako bi se ponovno povezala s Freddyjem, Bonnie, Chicom i Foxyjem, pokrećući zastrašujući niz događaja koji će otkriti mračne tajne o pravom podrijetlu Freddyjevog i osloboditi davno zaboravljeni užas skriven desetljećima."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"Fünf Nächte kann jeder überleben. Doch dieses Mal gibt es keine zweite Chance.","homepage":"https://www.upig.de/micro/five-nights-at-freddy-s-2","overview":"Sie sind nicht mehr nur bei Freddy’s … Seit den albtraumhaften Geschehnissen in Freddy’s Pizzeria ist ein Jahr vergangen. Die Geschichten darüber, was sich dort genau abgespielt hat, haben sich längst zu einem lokalen Mythos verklärt – ein Mythos, der so populär ist, dass die Stadt nun sogar das erste „Fazfest“ abhalten will. Der ehemalige Wachmann Mike und die Polizistin Vanessa haben Mikes elfjähriger Schwester Abby die Wahrheit über das Schicksal ihrer animatronischen Freunde bislang verschwiegen. Eines Tages schleicht sich Abby heimlich davon, um sich mit Freddy, Bonnie, Chica und Foxy zu treffen. Sie ahnt nicht, dass sie damit eine Reihe von schrecklichen Ereignissen in Gang setzt, die dunkle Geheimnisse über den Ursprung von Freddy’s Pizzeria enthüllen – und einen Schrecken entfesseln, der seit Jahrzehnten verborgen lag."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"П'ять ночей у Фредді 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"Будь-хто може протриматися п'ять ночей. Але цього разу — другого шансу не буде.","homepage":"","overview":"Через рік після надприродного кошмару в піцерії Freddy Fazbear's, те, що сталося, перетворилося на місцеву легенду легенда і надихнуло на перше в місті святкування Fazfest. Не знаючи правди, Еббі таємно вирушає до Фредді, Бонні, Чіки та Фоксі, запускає ланцюг моторошних подій, і стикається з похмурими секретами походження піцерії, пробуджуючи давній жах, прихований десятиліттями."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Pięć koszmarnych nocy 2","runtime":105,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Były ochroniarz Mike oraz policjantka Vanessa ukrywali przed 11-letnią siostrą Mike'a, Abby, prawdę o losie jej animatronicznych przyjaciół. Jednak gdy Abby wymyka się, by ponownie połączyć się z Freddy'm, Bonniem, Chicą i Foxym, uruchamia to przerażającą serię wydarzeń, które odkrywają mroczne sekrety związane z prawdziwym pochodzeniem Freddy'ego i uwalniają zapomniany horror, który był ukrywany przez dekady."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Piecas naktis pie Fredija 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Piecas naktis var izdzīvot jebkurš. Šoreiz otrās iespējas nebūs."},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"Non sono più solo da Freddy's.","homepage":"https://www.universalpictures.it/micro/five-nights-2#iframe1","overview":"È passato un anno dall'incubo soprannaturale alla Freddy Fazbear's Pizza. Le storie su ciò che è accaduto lì sono state trasformate in una leggenda locale che ha ispirato il primo Fazfest della città. L'ex guardia di sicurezza Mike (Josh Hutcherson) e l'agente di polizia Vanessa (Elizabeth Lail) hanno nascosto alla sorella undicenne di Mike, Abby (Piper Rubio), la verità sul destino dei suoi amici animatronici. Ma quando Abby sgattaiola fuori per ricongiungersi con Freddy, Bonnie, Chica e Foxy, si scatenerà una serie di eventi terrificanti, che riveleranno oscuri segreti sulla vera origine di Freddy's e sveleranno un orrore a lungo dimenticato e nascosto per decenni."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"חמישה לילות אצל פרדי 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"רמה חדשה של פחד.","homepage":"","overview":"מי ישרוד את הלילה? משחק המחשב המצמרר שהפך לתופעה תרבותית ולשובר קופות ענק – חוזר בדצמבר הקרוב להפחיד אתכם עד לעמקי נשמתכם."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Viis ööd Freddy baaris 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"Ma pole enam Freddy juures üksi.","homepage":"","overview":"Freddy Fazbeari pitsabaaris toimunud veresaunast on möödunud aasta. Endine pitsabaari turvamees Mike ja politseinik Vanessa varjavad tõde oma animatroonilistest sõprade saatuse kohta Mike'i 11-aastase õe Abby eest. Kui tüdruk jookseb uuesti Freddie, Bonnie, Chica ja Foxyga kohtuma, toob see kaasa hirmutavad tagajärjed."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"5 คืนสยองที่ร้านเฟรดดี้ 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ไมค์ และ วาเนสซ่า ได้พยายามทำทุกวิถีทางที่จะปกป้อง แอ็บบี้ จากความจริงเกี่ยวกับเพื่อน ๆ หุ่นแอนิมาโทรนิกของเธอ แต่เมื่อเธอแอบหนีออกไปหาพวกมัน การตัดสินใจของเธอก็ได้จุดไฟแห่งความสยองที่ไม่ควรจะถูกปลุกขึ้นมา"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"玩具熊的五夜驚魂 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"「費斯熊佛萊迪薄餅店」發生的噩夢過去一年，小鎮將恐怖慘劇扭曲成誇張傳説，大家甚至攞件事來韜光，舉辦首屆 Fazfest 極樂節日！前任保安員米奇、警官雲妮莎一直向妹妹艾比隱瞞恐怖真相，直至艾比偷偷出走，企圖與一眾電動玩偶朋友重聚，才意外觸發聯鎖恐怖事件，跟 Fazfest 更扯上莫大關係。深藏數十年的血腥秘密，隨即衝出薄餅店全面爆發！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Пять ночей с Фредди 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"«Вы здесь?»","homepage":"https://www.fivenightsatfreddys.movie/","overview":"Спустя год после сверхъестественного кошмара в пиццерии Freddy Fazbear's произошедшее превратилось в местную легенду и вдохновило на первое в городе празднование Fazfest. Не зная правды, Эбби тайно отправляется к Фредди, Бонни, Чике и Фокси, запускает цепь пугающих событий и сталкивается с мрачными секретами происхождения пиццерии, пробуждая давний ужас, скрытый десятилетиями."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Нощна смяна във \"Фреди\" 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"Всеки може да преживее пет нощи. Този път няма да има втори шанс.","homepage":"","overview":"Една година след свръхестествения кошмар в пицарията на Фреди Фазбър, историите за случилото се там са се превърнали в местна легенда, вдъхновяваща първия по рода си Фазфест в града. С истината за случилото се скрита от нея, Аби се промъква, за да се свърже отново с Фреди, Бони, Чика и Фокси, което задейства ужасяваща поредица от събития, които ще разкрият тъмни тайни за истинския произход на Фреди и ще освободят отдавна забравен ужас, скрит десетилетия наред."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Penkios naktys pas Fredį 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kiekvienas gali išgyventi penkias naktis. Šį kartą antros galimybės nebus."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Öt éjjel Freddy Pizzázójában 2.","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Egy év telt el a Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza falai között történt természetfeletti rémálom óta. Az ott történtek története mára eltúlzott, tábori hangulatú helyi legendává torzult, ami ihletet adott a város első Fazfestjének. Mivel előle eltitkolták az igazságot, Abby kiszökik otthonról, hogy újra találkozzon Freddyvel, Bonnie-val, Chicával és Foxyval. Ezzel azonban egy félelmetes eseménysorozatot indít el, amely sötét titkokat tár fel Freddy’s valódi eredetéről, és szabadjára enged egy évtizedek óta elrejtett, rég elfeledett borzalmat."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Viisi yötä Freddyllä 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"On kulunut vuosi Freddy Fazbear’s Pizzan yliluonnollisesta painajaisesta. Yön tapahtumista kertovat tarinat ovat muuttuneet paikalliseksi urbaanilegendaksi, joka on innoittanut kaupunkilaiset järjestämään ensimmäisen Fazfest-tapahtuman. Entinen yövartija Mike ja poliisi Vanessa ovat salanneet totuuden animatronisten eläinhahmojen kohtalosta Miken 11-vuotiaalta siskolta Abbylta. Kun Abby livahtaa tapaamaan ystäviään Freddyä, Bonnieta, Chicaa ja Foxya, käynnistyy kauhistuttava tapahtumasarja, joka paljastaa Freddy’sin synkän alkuperän ja päästää vuosikymmeniä uinuneen kauhun valloilleen."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Cinq nuits chez Freddy 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"T'es là?","homepage":"https://universalpictures.ca/fr/movie/cinq-nuits-chez-freddy-2/","overview":"Un an après les cauchemars surnaturels survenus chez Freddy, l'histoire de ce qui s'est passé là-bas s'est transformée en une légende locale, inspirant ainsi le tout premier FazFest de la ville. La vérité sur les événements lui étant cachée, Abby s'enfuit pour renouer avec Freddy, Bonnie, Chica et Foxy, déclenchant une série terrifiante d'événements. Cela va lui permettre de révéler de sombres secrets concernant les origines du restaurant et de libérer des horreur perdue depuis plusieurs dizaines d'années."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Um ano após o pesadelo sobrenatural na Freddy Fazbear's Pizza, as histórias sobre o que aconteceu lá foram transformadas numa lenda local exagerada, inspirando o primeiro Fazfest da cidade. Sem saber a verdade sobre o que aconteceu, Abby foge para se reencontrar com Freddy, Bonnie, Chica e Foxy, desencadeando uma série de eventos aterrorizantes que revelarão segredos obscuros sobre a verdadeira origem da Freddy's e libertarão um horror há muito esquecido, escondido durante décadas."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"佛萊迪餐館之五夜驚魂2","runtime":0,"tagline":"他們已經不在佛萊迪餐館了。","homepage":"https://www.universalpictures.tw/micro/five-nights-2","overview":"自從費斯熊佛萊迪披薩餐館發生的那場超自然噩夢事件已經過去一年，當時的恐怖事件逐漸被扭曲成誇張的當地傳說，甚至啟發小鎮舉辦史上首次的費斯節。前任夜間警衛麥克（喬許哈契遜 飾）以及警官凡妮莎（伊莉莎白萊爾 飾）向麥克11歲的妹妹艾碧（派珀魯比歐 飾）隱瞞關於她的機械玩偶朋友們的真相。但是當艾碧偷溜出去，再次找到佛萊迪、邦尼、積卡和霍斯後，又將發生一系列的恐怖駭人事件，揭露佛萊迪餐館真正起源的黑暗秘密，並且釋放一股隱藏數十年，早已被遺忘的邪惡力量。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":104,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mike,  een jongeman die het moeilijk heeft, neemt een baan aan als nachtwaker in het verlaten themarestaurant Freddy Fazbear’s Pizzeria in de hoop dat hij daarmee de voogdij over zijn zusje kan houden. Maar door die beslissing belandt hij diep in een duistere, bovennatuurlijke nachtmerrie."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ett år har gått sedan den övernaturliga mardrömmen på Freddy Fazbear's Pizza. Historierna om vad som hände där har förvandlats till en kitschig lokal legend som inspirerar staden till att hålla sin första Fazfest. Före detta säkerhetsvakten Mike och polisen Vanessa har undanhållit sanningen för Mikes 11-åriga syster, Abby, gällande hennes animatroniska vänners öde. Men när Abby smiter ut för att återförenas med Freddy, Bonnie, Chica och Foxy, sätter det igång en serie skräckinjagande händelser som avslöjar mörka hemligheter om Freddys ursprung och släpper lös en sedan länge bortglömd fasa som har hållits gömd i årtionden."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ett år etter det overnaturlige marerittet på Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza har historiene om hva som skjedde der blitt vridd om til en campy lokal legende, noe som inspirerer byens aller første Fazfest. Siden sannheten om hendelsene er holdt skjult for henne, sniker Abby seg ut for å gjenforenes med Freddy, Bonnie, Chica og Foxy. Det setter i gang en skremmende rekke hendelser som vil avsløre mørke hemmeligheter om Freddys egentlige opprinnelse – og slippe løs en lenge glemt gru som har vært skjult i flere tiår."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Pět nocí u Freddyho 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Od hrůzných událostí prvního dílu uplynul rok. Mike (Josh Hutcherson), bývalý noční hlídač zavřené pizzerie, tehdy s pomocí policistky Vanessy (Elizabeth Lail) zlikvidoval zloducha, který měnil animatronické loutky ve vraždící monstra. Mike tím zachránil život mladší sestře Abby (Piper Rubio), o níž se po smrti rodičů stará. Především díky němu si malá Abby neodnesla z „návštěvy“ Freddyho pizzerie žádné následky, naopak se jí po loutkových přátelích, Freddym, Bonnie, Chice a Foxy docela stýská. Dokonce tak, že se navzdory bratrovu zákazu do zavřeného podniku vydá, aby se s nimi znovu setkala. Tím nechtěně spustí nové kolo hrůzy. Tajemství Freddyho pizzerie je totiž mnohem krvavější a děsivější, než by se po prvním díle mohlo zdát. A pokud se zdejším stvůrám podaří přimět Abby ke spolupráci, budou se dít věci, a to nejen v prostorách samotné restaurace, ale v celém městě. Tahle noc bude zřejmě dlouhá a krvavá."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"خمس ليالٍ في فريدي 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"بعد مرور عام على الكابوس الخارق في مطعم فريدي فازبير، تحولت قصص ما جرى إلى أسطورة محلية ساخرة، مما ألهم تنظيم أول «فازفست» في البلدة. دون أن يُكشف لها الحقيقة، تنطلق آبي سرّاً لإعادة التواصل مع فريدي، بوني، تشيكا وفوكسي، لتبدأ سلسلة مرعبة من الأحداث التي ستكشف أسراراً مظلمة عن الأصل الحقيقي لمطعم فريدي، وتطلق رعباً منسيّاً كان مخفيّاً لعقود."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Πέντε Νύχτες στου Φρέντι 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"Δεν είναι πια μόνο στου Φρέντι","homepage":"","overview":"Ένας χρόνος έχει περάσει μετά τον μεταφυσικό εφιάλτη στην πιτσαρία του Φρέντι. Οι ιστορίες που κυκλοφορούν για όλα όσα συνέβησαν εκεί έχουν καθιερωθεί πια ως αστικοί μύθοι, δίνοντας έμπνευση για το πρώτο φεστιβάλ της πόλης αφιερωμένο στα σκοτεινά συμβάντα.  Ο πρώην φύλακας Μάικ και η αστυνομικός Βανέσσα έχουν αποκρύψει από τη 11χρονη αδελφή του Μάικ, Άμπι, την τύχη των ρομποτικών της φίλων.  Όταν όμως η Άμπι το σκάσει για να ξαναβρεί τον Φρέντι, την Μπόνι, την Τσίκα και τον Φόξι, θα πυροδοτήσει μία τρομαχτική αλληλουχία από γεγονότα.  Σκοτεινά μυστικά θα αποκαλυφθούν για την προέλευση της πιτσαρίας του Φρέντι και ένας από καιρό ξεχασμένος τρόμος θα εξαπολυθεί."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Pet noči pri Freddyju 2","runtime":104,"tagline":"Niso več samo pri Freddyju.","homepage":"https://www.fivenightsatfreddys.movie","overview":"Leto po nadnaravni nočni mori v Freddy Fazbear's Pizza so zgodbe o tem, kar se je tam zgodilo, popačene v ceneno lokalno legendo, ki je navdihnila prvi Fazfest v mestu. Ker ji je bila resnica prikrita, se Abby izmuzne, da bi se ponovno srečala s Freddyjem, Bonnie, Chico in Foxyjem, s čimer sproži grozljivo serijo dogodkov, ki bodo razkrili temne skrivnosti o resničnem izvoru Freddyjevega lokala in sprožili desetletja skrito grozo."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"پنج شب در رستوران فردی 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"جرمی فیتزجرالد در سال ۱۹۸۷، پس از زندگی‌ای پر فراز و نشیب، شغلی به‌عنوان نگهبان امنیتی در پیتزا فروشی جدید فرِدی فزبیِر پیدا کرد، اما با ورود به آنجا فهمید که همه چیز آن‌طور که به نظر می‌رسد نیست."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Fostul paznic Mike și agenta de poliție Vanessa au ascuns adevărul de sora de 11 ani a lui Mike, Abby, cu privire la soarta prietenilor ei animatronici. Dar când Abby fuge de acasă ca să se reîntâlnească cu Freddy, Bonnie, Chica și Foxy, declanșează o serie de evenimente înfricoșătoare care scot la iveală secrete întunecate despre adevărata origine a lui Freddy’s și eliberează o groază uitată, ascunsă de zeci de ani."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Пет ноћи код Фредија 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Годину дана од натприродне ноћне море у Фредијевој пицерији Фазбер, приче о томе шта се тамо догодило искривљене су у клишеирану локалну легенду, инспиришући први Фазфест у граду. Сакривена од истине, Еби се искрада да би се поново повезала са Фредијем, Бони, Чиком и Фокси, покрећући застрашујући низ догађаја који ће открити мрачне тајне о правом пореклу Фредијеве пицерије и ослободити деценијама скривени ужас."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Alle kan overleve fem nætter. Men denne gang vil ingen overleve."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"69343acffc039cd353b70ef1","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/69343acffc039cd353b70ef1","author":"PROREVIEW.FR","content":"⭐ Review of Five Nights at Freddy’s 2 ⭐\r\n\r\nFive Nights at Freddy’s 2 is simply excellent! The movie delivers incredible visual effects that keep you on edge from start to finish. I literally jumped 11 times, which shows how well the horror atmosphere is handled.\r\n\r\nCompared to the first film, this sequel is much better: more intense, more immersive, and with an amazing ending that truly surprised me. The actors are outstanding, fully bringing the story and the tension to life.\r\n\r\nFor me, it’s a solid 8/10.\r\n\r\n🔻 Negative points\r\n\r\nEven though the movie is great, I was expecting more fights and more challenges to push the tension even further. With a bit more action, it could have been nearly perfect.","created_at":"2025-12-06T14:16:47.107Z","updated_at":"2025-12-06T17:07:52.235Z","author_details":{"name":"PROREVIEW.FR","rating":10,"username":"oheohematelot","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"6935a83654a2f5f2f6243e98","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6935a83654a2f5f2f6243e98","author":"MontyTG","content":"**Weaker than the original film but entertaining.** \r\n\r\nAs a massive fan of the original film, and would go as far as to say it's a misunderstood masterpiece. This slightly disappointed me. The runtime was way too short for a film this ambitious, and it doesn't seem to know what to focus on. It feels like subplot after subplot that barely progress the story until the final act. Then it rushes through everything with an ending that feels abrupt. It's a shame because the Marionette/Charlotte plotline is brilliant, the final 30 minutes are chaotic and entertaining, and the Toy animatronics are given justice. Overall, a really entertaining time with an incredible score, but the story needs more attention.","created_at":"2025-12-07T16:15:50.643Z","updated_at":"2025-12-07T16:15:50.650Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"MontyTG","avatar_path":"/yNwWtAd10wydhvWqvJX4tbxq3KC.jpg"}},{"id":"6935ba75af7a103a92d1ffae","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6935ba75af7a103a92d1ffae","author":"LegendGamerXZ","content":"I think this movie is what a FNAF Movie should be, way better then the first, it really dives into the horror, it’s also a bigger film, the cinematography has dramatically improved, and so many Easter eggs that the diehard fans will catch on, but some you will miss in a blink of an eye. The animatronics were awesome and that is thanks to the Jim Henson Corporation. The voices were very well done as well, if any of you were doubting Megan Fox as Toy Chica, she did well. It sounds like Toy Chica and also made it her own, and MatPat’s voice was very unrecognizable as Toy Bonnie. Kellen Goff was amazing like always. My only real gripe was the movie is really fast paced and it could have benefited with a longer runtime, and some of the writing and dialogue delivery was pretty wack in some parts of the film. That ending tho, it ended with a big cliffhanger and stay for the post credits, it’s insane. This movie is a huge improvement compared to the first movie.","created_at":"2025-12-07T17:33:41.702Z","updated_at":"2025-12-15T05:30:38.214Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":9,"username":"LegendGamerXZ","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"6936fca491e3d4c0ebf7c891","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6936fca491e3d4c0ebf7c891","author":"IMDB","content":"My Review of FNAF 2\r\nHonestly, the movie was absolutely incredible, especially for long-time fans of the franchise. I jumped more than nine times — no joke — and the special effects were on another level. The animatronics looked terrifying in the best possible way, and the actors did an amazing job bringing the story to life.\r\n\r\nOn the downside, the plot can be a bit hard to follow at times, and some moments feel a little confusing if you’re not familiar with the lore.\r\nBut overall, it was a thrilling experience, packed with tension, atmosphere, and fan-service done right.\r\n\r\nI’d easily rate it 8/10 or even higher. A must-see for any FNAF fan!\r\n\r\n","created_at":"2025-12-08T16:28:20.181Z","updated_at":"2025-12-08T16:30:10.128Z","author_details":{"name":"IMDB","rating":10,"username":"IMDBofficiellaccount","avatar_path":"/tem9LYNDSgxmj3pYjbz6xROM7ZX.png"}},{"id":"693b0a822da9fa1f716ec01f","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/693b0a822da9fa1f716ec01f","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-12-11T18:16:34.445Z","updated_at":"2025-12-11T19:38:52.629Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}},{"id":"695de2ddec235d59f83e61bb","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/695de2ddec235d59f83e61bb","author":"zdjacobobo","content":"$12","created_at":"2026-01-07T04:36:45.355Z","updated_at":"2026-01-07T13:46:19.058Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":null,"username":"zdjacobobo","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":104480,"adult":false,"title":"Divers at Work on the Wreck of the \"Maine\"","video":false,"overview":"Divers go to work on a wrecked ship (the battleship Maine that was blown up in Havana harbour during the Spanish-American War), surrounded by curiously disproportionate fish.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3297,"vote_count":142,"poster_path":"/duiuY8xi0fPCBegpWyToUQiZYSX.jpg","release_date":"1898-01-01","vote_average":5.697,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Visite sous-marine du Maine","original_language":"fr"},{"id":63663,"adult":false,"title":"Maine-Ocean Express","video":false,"overview":"\"Maine-Ocean\" is the name of a train that rides from Paris to Saint-Nazaire (near the ocean). In that train, Dejanira, a Brazilian, has a brush with the two ticket inspectors. Mimi, another traveler and also a lawyer, helps her. The four of them will meet together later and live a few shifted adventures with a strange-speaking sailor (Mimi's client).","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4923,"vote_count":121,"poster_path":"/rozC3lvWxHld3ux5OxrSXwtJP6V.jpg","release_date":"1986-04-16","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/btQ6O8mJyxpYsVF3OKYQnkh3pge.jpg","original_title":"Maine Océan","original_language":"fr"},{"id":198556,"adult":false,"title":"Main Krishna Hoon","video":false,"overview":"In answer to an orphan boy's prayers, the divine Lord Krishna comes to Earth, befriends the boy, and helps him find a loving family.","genre_ids":[16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5476,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/4fddOiJPp4Mf0jFXcp2WE8qvNW2.jpg","release_date":"2013-01-25","vote_average":6.018,"backdrop_path":"/1WCES8hj3IQ086iWM1XOEeb5jvL.jpg","original_title":"मैं कृष्णा हूँ","original_language":"hi"},{"id":13679,"adult":false,"title":"Kirikou and the Wild Beasts","video":false,"overview":"Kirikou's Grandfather says that the story of Kirikou and The Witch was too short, so he proceeds to explain more about Kirikou's accomplishments. We find out how little boy became a gardener, a detective, a maker of pottery, a merchant, a traveler and a doctor.","genre_ids":[12,16,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7853,"vote_count":316,"poster_path":"/yPWBxCxwMbwdvwcXagHNOPWrCig.jpg","release_date":"2005-12-07","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/ggDcngtIQVXMQAsK0ucYbmi59Bv.jpg","original_title":"Kirikou et les bêtes sauvages","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1031905,"adult":false,"title":"Moments: Six","video":false,"overview":"A serial killer and the detective who tracked him down find themselves in an unexpected stalemate.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1622,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/pgd1mxPKwEddtst65yzGN0KATBl.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-03","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/lGtHZ2gLJhB3LUxjLSDR3fY7hcx.jpg","original_title":"Moments: Six","original_language":"en"},{"id":542784,"adult":false,"title":"Operation Thai Cave Rescue","video":false,"overview":"Thai cave Rescue documents the dramatic rescue of 12 boys and their soccer coach from the Tham Luang Cave in northern Thailand. Featuring interviews with key people involved, the film explains how the boys became trapped in the cave by heavy rains on Saturday, June 23, 2018, and explains how, fearing the worst, relatives and local rescuers began searching for the boys but to no avail. Finally, the film reveals how an international team of rescuers was called upon to find the boys and ultimately bring them to safety. This remarkable story gripped the world for 18 days. A stunning example of innovation, teamwork and human endurance in one of the most hostile environments on earth - a flooded cave.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1342,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/1ibkgLrUx5K2Ejoij3VkAJgnCCh.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-13","vote_average":8.9,"backdrop_path":"/5u25dUUeCNdsaGp0VeFNbRstoTg.jpg","original_title":"Operation Thai Cave Rescue","original_language":"en"},{"id":262903,"adult":false,"title":"Main Tera Hero","video":false,"overview":"Seenu loves Sunaina but they're chased by a stalking cop, an infatuated beauty and her mafia don dad - can Seenu's heroics work?","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4194,"vote_count":192,"poster_path":"/bupZH3i1SAaLLC0OgYMSLDZN63Q.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-04","vote_average":5.667,"backdrop_path":"/wgYx4MwezeoAkRVAJsYdOMAMeWC.jpg","original_title":"मैं तेरा हीरो","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1059116,"adult":false,"title":"g","video":true,"overview":"A disgruntled couple sets on a road trip, as the boyfriend is hiding something mysterious from his girlfriend. The suspicion grows bigger when she begins to fear her boyfriends next move.","genre_ids":[9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0618,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"g","original_language":"en"},{"id":267583,"adult":false,"title":"Disney Presents: Main Street Electrical Parade - Farewell Season","video":false,"overview":"Catch the spark after dark at Disneyland Park. And say farewell to one of the Magic Kingdom's most celebrated traditions - The Main Street Electrical Parade. Where else, but in The Main Street Electrical Parade, could you see an illuminated 40-foot-long fire-breathing dragon? And hear the energy of its legendary melody one last time? It's unforgettable after-dark magic that will glow in your heart long after the last float has disappeared.","genre_ids":[99,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2044,"vote_count":75,"poster_path":"/lRyfmbHKFcQxUeboRmJVIZBx6kF.jpg","release_date":"1996-11-25","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/f1MplKJl4LveJJOa7JsirLtf3NR.jpg","original_title":"Disney Presents: Main Street Electrical Parade - Farewell Season","original_language":"en"},{"id":44874,"adult":false,"title":"Barbie: A Fashion Fairytale","video":false,"overview":"Barbie, a popular actress on a sabbatical, 