ey, a group of college students accidentally unleash the imp -- a sadistic little spirit that creates demons and loves sexy women.","genre_ids":[35,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.599,"vote_count":134,"poster_path":"/2I7yv8T9rX1C1cBtJOrdOxoh7W3.jpg","release_date":"1988-01-29","vote_average":4.728,"backdrop_path":"/eWK7RcC5h5l98q2LKK68b6R76Ir.jpg","original_title":"Sorority Babes in the Slimeball Bowl-O-Rama","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":161,"adult":false,"title":"Ocean's Eleven","video":false,"overview":"Less than 24 hours into his parole, charismatic thief Danny Ocean is already rolling out his next plan: In one night, Danny's hand-picked crew of specialists will attempt to steal more than $150 million from three Las Vegas casinos. But to score the cash, Danny risks his chances of reconciling with ex-wife, Tess.","genre_ids":[53,80],"popularity":9.3725,"vote_count":12338,"poster_path":"/hQQCdZrsHtZyR6NbKH2YyCqd2fR.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-07","vote_average":7.455,"backdrop_path":"/ncoqdHs1poUaBqyKic9YI8ai7MP.jpg","original_title":"Ocean's Eleven","original_language":"en"},{"id":163,"adult":false,"title":"Ocean's Twelve","video":false,"overview":"Despite pulling off one of the biggest heists in Las Vegas history and splitting the $160 million take, each of the infamous Ocean's crew have tried to go straight, lay low and live a legit life ... but that's proven to be a challenge. Casino owner Terry Benedict demands that Danny Ocean return the money, plus millions more in interest. Unable to come up the cash, the crew is forced to come together to pull off another series of heists, this time in Rome, Paris, and Amsterdam – but a Europol agent is hot on their heels.","genre_ids":[53,80],"popularity":5.8129,"vote_count":7751,"poster_path":"/pE5anFf7nf6ah7V3VRezQ1KSovi.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-09","vote_average":6.565,"backdrop_path":"/5b5HrewiViLWEdMR4dmbd7ajQ8Q.jpg","original_title":"Ocean's Twelve","original_language":"en"},{"id":590164,"adult":false,"title":"Mercy Black","video":false,"overview":"A woman is sent to a mental institution after stabbing her classmate in an attempt to conjure an evil spirit called, Mercy Black. Fifteen years later she's released, and must save her nephew, who has become obsessed with the phenomenon.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"popularity":0.5438,"vote_count":229,"poster_path":"/6e0eblwQS11J5ZBb5PNoigCKWGB.jpg","release_date":"2019-03-24","vote_average":5.959,"backdrop_path":"/rVyaYSUr9K9BxpRj748Ceft3MYK.jpg","original_title":"Mercy Black","original_language":"en"},{"id":763563,"adult":false,"title":"Unboxing Ibai","video":false,"overview":"Esports streamer Ibai Llanos hacks the first unboxing of the new PS5 on Twitch, the world’s leading gaming platform. What initially appears to be a conventional streaming event becomes the first horror film ever produced, executed, and broadcast live, utilising a total of nine cameras, a production crew of seventy people, and an amazing display of live special effects.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":1.8587,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/ebiGDHDePiX7Vgrfc5xlfPGlkFy.jpg","release_date":"2020-11-24","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/sy8EwKlR5Hp6Iel08N18a0gUlVO.jpg","original_title":"Unboxing Ibai","original_language":"es"},{"id":1291785,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: Dragon Throne","video":false,"overview":"The second installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.\r In 1950s Hong Kong, brothers Lui Cheng-tung and Chen Jim fled to the lawless Kowloon Walled City at the peak of their careers. They endured hardships, waiting for a chance to reclaim their losses. During this time, they encountered a man who significantly influenced their struggle to regain what they had lost.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,12],"popularity":0.7488,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之龍頭","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1291787,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: The Final Chapter","video":false,"overview":"The final installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":0.2766,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之終章","original_language":"cn"},{"id":657,"adult":false,"title":"From Russia with Love","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 is back in the second installment of the James Bond series, this time battling a secret crime organization known as SPECTRE. Russians Rosa Klebb and Kronsteen are out to snatch a decoding device known as the Lektor, using the ravishing Tatiana to lure Bond into helping them. Bond willingly travels to meet Tatiana in Istanbul, where he must rely on his wits to escape with his life in a series of deadly encounters with the enemy.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":6.5294,"vote_count":3278,"poster_path":"/zx4V17FP8oclNvOpTgs2iCCtiYk.jpg","release_date":"1963-10-10","vote_average":7.065,"backdrop_path":"/8JMiQa0OqsCYvbNUrQIrMzwV7g2.jpg","original_title":"From Russia with Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":658,"adult":false,"title":"Goldfinger","video":false,"overview":"Special agent 007 comes face to face with one of the most notorious villains of all time, and now he must outwit and outgun the powerful tycoon to prevent him from cashing in on a devious scheme to raid Fort Knox -- and obliterate the world's economy.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":6.2145,"vote_count":3869,"poster_path":"/aKNFzaqQgPzsGXnsMc4kJH5hFIV.jpg","release_date":"1964-09-20","vote_average":7.355,"backdrop_path":"/f1Is9VLQZSRpeLMU7mIcj5aXclt.jpg","original_title":"Goldfinger","original_language":"en"},{"id":668,"adult":false,"title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","video":false,"overview":"With the help of Marc-Ange Draco, head of the Unione Corse crime syndicate, and Draco's troubled daughter Tracy, James Bond tracks his archnemesi